  <div class="card" id="card"></div>

  <script>
    const cards = [
      "Bank Error in Your Favour: You gain DOUBLE POINTS for locking this station.",
      "Roll a One: For your next journey you may only progress one stop along your chosen tube line. Then you must either switch lines or attempt to lock that station.",
      "Go Directly to Jail: Do not pass GO. Do not collect Â£200. Proceed Immediately to Tower Hill Station, you do not claim any stations you pass along the way. At Tower Hill you MUST disembark the train. You may not claim Tower Hill while there.",
